1
00:00:00,266 --> 00:00:01,366
welcome back

2
00:00:01,366 --> 00:00:05,866
today we are going to see what it takes to get a good source of dragon blood

3
00:00:05,900 --> 00:00:07,233
more specifically

4
00:00:07,233 --> 00:00:09,700
how to get the draconic fusion crafter

5
00:00:09,766 --> 00:00:14,000
that thing requires end game materials from all of the magic mods

6
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,666
so let's get started from the first item

7
00:00:16,666 --> 00:00:18,866
the bloody ichorium fusion casing

8
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:22,666
and all magic mods are rebalanced around thaumcraft

9
00:00:22,833 --> 00:00:24,033
so here we are

10
00:00:24,266 --> 00:00:25,800
after getting a witches oven

11
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:29,166
we start extracting random breaths from saplings

12
00:00:29,366 --> 00:00:31,633
then we farm some questionable plants

13
00:00:31,633 --> 00:00:34,466
to get the ingredients to make a nice soup

14
00:00:34,666 --> 00:00:36,566
okay just kidding

15
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,900
that's not edible

16
00:00:38,066 --> 00:00:40,233
we just made some compost

17
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:42,400
a really weird compost

18
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:45,000
since instead of growing plants

19
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,300
it mutates them

20
00:00:46,666 --> 00:00:50,500
and those mutated plants will give off a whiff of magic when burned

21
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:53,500
which is required for an attuned stone

22
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:55,600
required to craft Greg's altar

23
00:00:55,633 --> 00:00:58,666
thus finally allowing us to start blood magic

24
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,600
this is a really funny mod

25
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:03,300
that is all about taking blood tests

26
00:01:03,466 --> 00:01:05,766
you just have to keep puncturing yourself

27
00:01:05,766 --> 00:01:07,833
until you almost faint out

28
00:01:08,833 --> 00:01:12,900
and then we soak items inside that pool of tomato sauce

29
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:16,600
however all of those blood losses are not healthy

30
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:21,166
so we made a personal healing nano booster to keep in check

31
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,666
and we charge it wirelessly

32
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,000
with that

33
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,433
we can now have some peak game play

34
00:01:28,100 --> 00:01:32,633
just look at how much life essence of mouse with a weight stuck on it is making

35
00:01:33,366 --> 00:01:37,100
we just have to change the items in the chest every now and then

36
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:39,766
until we rush the whole tier 5 altar

37
00:01:40,666 --> 00:01:41,766
but then we find out

38
00:01:41,766 --> 00:01:45,266
we also have to do other things for our dragon blood blocks

39
00:01:45,266 --> 00:01:47,000
but since we are blind

40
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,600
and can't see there's a missing chalk

41
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:52,200
we shall go back to witchery in frustration

42
00:01:52,633 --> 00:01:55,066
here we rush an altar to power the distillery

43
00:01:55,066 --> 00:01:57,466
we rushed without taking recordings

44
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,000
but to do some quests

45
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,000
we make a kettle

46
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,466
and start brewing some potions of love

47
00:02:03,966 --> 00:02:06,633
which is somehow part of a sleeping potion

48
00:02:06,866 --> 00:02:08,766
guess you gotta love sleeping

49
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:11,300
and after taking a nice sip

50
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:13,100
we lose all of our stuff

51
00:02:13,766 --> 00:02:18,833
and I don't understand how that's a nightmare any more than doing those magic mods

52
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:20,266
anyways

53
00:02:20,266 --> 00:02:24,600
that didn't seem to be required for getting what we needed some chalks

54
00:02:24,666 --> 00:02:27,500
so we just skip quests and get those

55
00:02:28,066 --> 00:02:30,400
which we use to make a ritual helper

56
00:02:30,866 --> 00:02:33,033
which isn't really helping much

57
00:02:33,466 --> 00:02:35,633
anyways after figuring it out

58
00:02:35,633 --> 00:02:37,866
we managed to make the magic circle appear

59
00:02:37,866 --> 00:02:40,100
and produce a blood powered sword

60
00:02:40,566 --> 00:02:42,866
with that we collect some weak shards

61
00:02:42,866 --> 00:02:44,800
that will be required later on

62
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:48,700
then to stop having to do peak gameplay

63
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:50,566
we build the well of suffering

64
00:02:51,166 --> 00:02:53,633
that thing will make blood using mobs

65
00:02:53,766 --> 00:02:56,000
and it can even work with a mob farm

66
00:02:56,433 --> 00:03:00,666
finally we no longer have to stuck ourselves onto that annoying thing

67
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:04,100
and we move it below our main altar

68
00:03:04,866 --> 00:03:05,066
now

69
00:03:05,066 --> 00:03:07,800
while our blood passively builds up

70
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,633
we can go summon a demon

71
00:03:09,666 --> 00:03:12,633
so that we can kill him to get some shards

72
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:13,633
next

73
00:03:13,633 --> 00:03:15,566
we start melting random stuff

74
00:03:15,566 --> 00:03:17,666
to make some colorful lamps

75
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,366
which we place on our newly built altar

76
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,266
once every lamp shoots the center

77
00:03:24,266 --> 00:03:26,066
we can start the new ritual

78
00:03:26,066 --> 00:03:27,966
the convocation of the damned

79
00:03:28,866 --> 00:03:31,233
and when the pyrotechnics are done

80
00:03:31,233 --> 00:03:33,633
we can sacrifice a demon on top of it

81
00:03:33,633 --> 00:03:37,800
thus creating a portal that will start building an ever expanding town

82
00:03:38,366 --> 00:03:40,033
this place will spawn the demons

83
00:03:40,033 --> 00:03:42,066
that will drop the shards we needed

84
00:03:42,066 --> 00:03:44,566
and since we will need a lot

85
00:03:44,566 --> 00:03:47,433
we set up an industrial mob farm for those

86
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,766
the first usage will be making an ichorium block

87
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:53,633
which we soak into blood right away

88
00:03:54,633 --> 00:03:57,600
and that was the first part of our draconic crafter

89
00:03:57,866 --> 00:03:59,366
the second one is more neat

90
00:03:59,366 --> 00:04:02,233
and requires the funny flower mod by Vazkii

91
00:04:02,766 --> 00:04:04,600
so we start making a stone pot

92
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,833
for watering the funny flowers

93
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:11,766
we use that to merge some random flowers into other flowers

94
00:04:12,466 --> 00:04:15,633
and the first mutated flower should be a pure daisy

95
00:04:15,633 --> 00:04:17,833
which can enchant blocks around it

96
00:04:18,366 --> 00:04:19,866
with those new blocks

97
00:04:19,866 --> 00:04:23,600
we can craft a mana pool where we can't even swim

98
00:04:24,033 --> 00:04:25,300
and a mana spreader

99
00:04:25,366 --> 00:04:28,066
that will concentrate mana into beams

100
00:04:28,466 --> 00:04:31,100
with those two and a couple more of flowers

101
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:33,366
we start filling up our pool with mana

102
00:04:33,766 --> 00:04:36,500
and I have no idea if this is even working

103
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:38,500
or how much mana we are making

104
00:04:38,833 --> 00:04:42,033
but the real question here is why we are doing that

105
00:04:42,233 --> 00:04:43,133
never mind

106
00:04:43,133 --> 00:04:44,433
let's follow the guide

107
00:04:44,433 --> 00:04:47,233
to get the gaia plate for our draconic crafter

108
00:04:47,633 --> 00:04:50,300
after throwing stuff into our mana pool

109
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:52,400
it turns more bluish in color

110
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:56,566
and that blue stuff was needed for our combustion generator plant

111
00:04:57,066 --> 00:04:59,733
that plants turns burnable fuels into mana

112
00:04:59,733 --> 00:05:02,266
at the price of lag and items despawned

113
00:05:02,966 --> 00:05:05,700
however that Mana was still not enough

114
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:08,666
luckily Asgardandelion came in and help

115
00:05:08,666 --> 00:05:11,066
with a nice plant that does not cause lag

116
00:05:11,066 --> 00:05:13,033
nor other annoying things

117
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:15,966
next instead of filling a pool

118
00:05:15,966 --> 00:05:19,400
we use our mana on an altar to craft runes

119
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,633
and here we have some more peak gameplay

120
00:05:22,633 --> 00:05:30,266
watching random items jumping around a stone while taking shots from some random wood contraptions feeding from random flowers

121
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:34,000
and since we are going to do this just a dozen of times

122
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,633
all with different recipes

123
00:05:35,633 --> 00:05:40,200
I see no point in even looking into if there is a way of automating that thing

124
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,566
once it starts sparkling

125
00:05:42,566 --> 00:05:45,600
we can throw in a rock and complete the process

126
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:49,566
we repeat that funny peek gameplay process for 50 times

127
00:05:49,566 --> 00:05:51,700
4 for each rune we can make

128
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:55,166
and then we hope we will never ever have to do that ever again

129
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:58,366
once we have all the runes set on the thumcraft altar

130
00:05:58,366 --> 00:06:02,000
we infuse those into a terrestrial agglomeration plane

131
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:04,000
which once again

132
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,066
will ask us to drop four items on it

133
00:06:06,066 --> 00:06:11,233
and hope they don't despawn before the process of unknown duration is completed

134
00:06:11,566 --> 00:06:12,866
to avoid risks

135
00:06:12,866 --> 00:06:14,666
we instead use a pool as a buffer

136
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:17,500
and some sparks to make random lights turn on

137
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:20,966
so that we can lag in FPS other than TPS

138
00:06:21,266 --> 00:06:23,800
and that yielded us some Terra steel

139
00:06:24,033 --> 00:06:28,266
and we had to spam a lot of things to make more at a decent speed

140
00:06:28,766 --> 00:06:32,266
and the thing we use that Terra Steel for is an elven portal

141
00:06:32,266 --> 00:06:36,066
which is a portal that we throw trash in to get some trash out

142
00:06:36,533 --> 00:06:37,866
with that new trash

143
00:06:37,866 --> 00:06:42,033
we can craft the gaia pylon required to summon on annoying boss

144
00:06:42,366 --> 00:06:44,033
unlike the rest of the mod

145
00:06:44,033 --> 00:06:47,433
this boss doesn't have any color or cool looking particle

146
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:51,366
and it is also immune to projectiles for some reason

147
00:06:51,833 --> 00:06:53,033
after defeating it

148
00:06:53,033 --> 00:06:55,366
we are rewarded with some gaia spirit

149
00:06:55,366 --> 00:06:58,200
which we use to make our frist gaia spirit ingot

150
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:00,666
and summon a friend of the previous boss

151
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:04,433
and now we just farm more of those annoying things

152
00:07:04,433 --> 00:07:09,433
until we have enough for the dense gaia plate required for our draconic fusion crafter

153
00:07:09,966 --> 00:07:12,000
once we build the new machine

154
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,300
we quickly make one ender dragon egg

155
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:14,966
then

156
00:07:14,966 --> 00:07:18,366
we can make the dragon blood out of mundane materials

157
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
but once we tried to do so

158
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,566
we run into an issue

159
00:07:22,566 --> 00:07:25,033
we need to bring this machine up to tier 3

160
00:07:25,866 --> 00:07:28,433
that requires wyvern fusion casings

161
00:07:28,433 --> 00:07:30,166
which we can almost do

162
00:07:30,366 --> 00:07:32,200
the main issue there is that

163
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:35,500
we need a mining module mk3 for our space elevator

164
00:07:36,566 --> 00:07:39,433
and while crafting that was an easy task

165
00:07:39,433 --> 00:07:40,100
to use it

166
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:43,666
we also need MK3 space elevator motors

167
00:07:44,433 --> 00:07:47,666
and those are going to require a couple of weird materials

168
00:07:47,666 --> 00:07:51,500
which we shall make in an appropriate sci-fi high tech episode

169
00:07:51,866 --> 00:07:54,066
so what's the lesson there

170
00:07:54,866 --> 00:07:56,500
yeah after all

171
00:07:56,500 --> 00:08:00,366
maybe bees are not that annoying to make use or manage

172
00:08:00,766 --> 00:08:02,166
and they are also evolving

173
00:08:02,166 --> 00:08:04,366
and starting to make electronics

174
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:07,366
so see you next season for motor bee

175
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,866
bye bye

176
00:00:00,266 --> 00:00:01,366
欢迎回来！

177
00:00:01,366 --> 00:00:05,866
今天我们来找找龙血的优秀来源

178
00:00:05,900 --> 00:00:07,233
更具体地说

179
00:00:07,233 --> 00:00:09,700
是要获得龙研聚合装置

180
00:00:09,766 --> 00:00:14,000
那东西需要所有魔法mod的最终材料

181
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:16,666
所以让我们从第一项开始

182
00:00:16,666 --> 00:00:18,866
血腥灵宝聚合机械方块

183
00:00:19,100 --> 00:00:22,666
所有魔法mod都围绕神秘时代魔改了

184
00:00:22,833 --> 00:00:24,033
来吧

185
00:00:24,266 --> 00:00:25,800
在得到女巫烤箱后

186
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:29,166
我们开始从树苗中提取随机熏气

187
00:00:29,366 --> 00:00:31,633
然后种植一些奇异植物

188
00:00:31,633 --> 00:00:34,466
来获得一碗美味汤料的配料

189
00:00:34,666 --> 00:00:36,566
好吧，开玩笑的

190
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:37,900
那可不能吃

191
00:00:38,066 --> 00:00:40,233
我们刚做了些堆肥

192
00:00:40,600 --> 00:00:42,400
一种非常奇怪的堆肥

193
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:45,000
因为它不催熟作物

194
00:00:45,000 --> 00:00:46,300
而是让其变异

195
00:00:46,666 --> 00:00:50,500
那些变异的植物在燃烧时会产生魔力之息

196
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:53,500
这是调谐之石所必需的

197
00:00:53,500 --> 00:00:55,600
用来制造血魔法祭坛

198
00:00:55,633 --> 00:00:58,666
这样我们就可以开始血魔法了

199
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,600
这是一个非常有趣/奇怪/幽默的mod

200
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:03,300
全是关于抽血化验的

201
00:01:03,466 --> 00:01:05,766
你只需要持续刺伤自己

202
00:01:05,766 --> 00:01:07,833
直到几乎晕倒

203
00:01:08,833 --> 00:01:12,900
然后我们把东西浸泡在番茄酱池里

204
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:16,600
然而，失血对健康不好

205
00:01:17,200 --> 00:01:21,166
所以我们做了个个人治疗纳米加速器来保持健康

206
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,666
并给它无线充电

207
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,000
有了那个

208
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:27,433
我们可以来点高端操作

209
00:01:28,100 --> 00:01:32,633
看看通过压着鼠标产生了多少生命精华

210
00:01:33,366 --> 00:01:37,100
我们只需要时不时地更换箱子里的物品

211
00:01:37,100 --> 00:01:39,766
直到我们速通五级祭坛

212
00:01:40,666 --> 00:01:41,766
但后来我们发现

213
00:01:41,766 --> 00:01:45,266
我们还要为龙血块做其他事情

214
00:01:45,266 --> 00:01:47,000
但因为我们视力不好

215
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:49,600
没看到少了一个粉笔痕迹

216
00:01:49,600 --> 00:01:52,200
我们沮丧地回到巫术中

217
00:01:52,633 --> 00:01:55,066
在这里，我们冲一个祭坛来为酿酒厂供电

218
00:01:55,066 --> 00:01:57,466
这里没有记录下来

219
00:01:58,000 --> 00:02:00,000
但是要做一些任务

220
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,000
我们做一个水壶

221
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:03,466
开始酿造一些爱之酿药水

222
00:02:03,966 --> 00:02:06,633
这是安眠药的一部分

223
00:02:06,866 --> 00:02:08,766
我猜你一定喜欢睡觉

224
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:11,300
喝了一口后

225
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:13,100
我们失去了所有的东西

226
00:02:13,766 --> 00:02:15,100
这是个噩梦

227
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:18,833
但比不上玩这些魔法mod噩梦

228
00:02:19,500 --> 00:02:20,266
不管怎样

229
00:02:20,266 --> 00:02:22,300
结果那些好像根本没必要

230
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:24,566
我们要的不过就是几支粉笔

231
00:02:24,666 --> 00:02:27,500
所以我们跳过任务去拿那些

232
00:02:28,066 --> 00:02:30,400
我们用它来做仪式帮手

233
00:02:30,866 --> 00:02:33,033
这并没有多大帮助

234
00:02:33,466 --> 00:02:35,633
反正弄清楚后

235
00:02:35,633 --> 00:02:37,866
我们设法让魔法阵出现了

236
00:02:37,866 --> 00:02:40,100
制造一把由血驱动的剑

237
00:02:40,566 --> 00:02:42,866
我们用它收集一些虚弱气血碎片

238
00:02:42,866 --> 00:02:44,800
以后会用得到

239
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:48,700
为了结束顶级游戏体验

240
00:02:48,700 --> 00:02:50,566
我们建造苦难之井

241
00:02:51,166 --> 00:02:53,633
那东西会利用生物制造血

242
00:02:53,766 --> 00:02:56,000
它甚至可以与工业屠宰场合作

243
00:02:56,433 --> 00:03:00,666
我们终于不用再做烦人的抽血了

244
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:04,100
我们把它移到主祭坛下面

245
00:03:04,866 --> 00:03:05,066
现在

246
00:03:05,066 --> 00:03:07,800
当我们的血液被动地积聚

247
00:03:07,800 --> 00:03:09,633
我们可以去召唤恶魔

248
00:03:09,666 --> 00:03:12,633
杀掉他获得一些碎片

249
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:13,800
接下来

250
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,566
我们开始融化乱七八糟的物品

251
00:03:15,566 --> 00:03:17,666
做一些五颜六色的灯

252
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:21,366
放在我们新建的祭坛上

253
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,266
一旦每盏灯都射向中心

254
00:03:24,266 --> 00:03:26,066
我们可以开始新的仪式

255
00:03:26,066 --> 00:03:27,966
恶魔入侵

256
00:03:28,866 --> 00:03:31,233
烟火表演结束后

257
00:03:31,233 --> 00:03:33,633
我们可以在上面献祭一个恶魔

258
00:03:33,633 --> 00:03:37,800
产生一个会不断扩建城镇的传送门

259
00:03:38,366 --> 00:03:40,033
这地方会滋生恶魔

260
00:03:40,033 --> 00:03:42,066
恶魔掉落我们需要的碎片

261
00:03:42,066 --> 00:03:44,566
既然我们需要很多

262
00:03:44,566 --> 00:03:47,433
我们为他们建立工业屠宰场

263
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:50,766
第一个用途是灵宝块

264
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:53,633
马上把它浸泡在血液里

265
00:03:54,633 --> 00:03:57,600
这是我们龙研的第一部分

266
00:03:57,866 --> 00:03:59,366
第二个更整洁

267
00:03:59,366 --> 00:04:02,233
需要Vazkii制作的奇怪花朵mod

268
00:04:02,766 --> 00:04:04,600
所以我们开始做一个石锅

269
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:06,833
给奇怪的花浇水

270
00:04:07,700 --> 00:04:11,766
我们用它来把一些杂七杂八的花合并成其他的花

271
00:04:12,466 --> 00:04:15,633
第一朵变异的花是白雏菊

272
00:04:15,633 --> 00:04:17,833
它可以把周围的方块转换

273
00:04:18,366 --> 00:04:19,866
用这些新方块

274
00:04:19,866 --> 00:04:23,600
我们可以做一个浅得不能游泳的魔力池

275
00:04:24,033 --> 00:04:25,300
和魔力发射器

276
00:04:25,366 --> 00:04:28,066
来将魔力聚焦成束流

277
00:04:28,466 --> 00:04:31,100
有了这两个方块和一些花朵

278
00:04:31,100 --> 00:04:33,366
可以开始填满魔力池了

279
00:04:33,766 --> 00:04:36,500
我不知道这是否在工作

280
00:04:36,500 --> 00:04:38,500
或者已经有了多少魔力

281
00:04:38,833 --> 00:04:42,033
但真正的问题是我们为什么要这么做

282
00:04:42,233 --> 00:04:43,133
没关系

283
00:04:43,133 --> 00:04:44,433
让我们跟随任务书

284
00:04:44,433 --> 00:04:47,233
来获得龙研要的盖亚板

285
00:04:47,633 --> 00:04:50,300
把东西扔进法力池后

286
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:52,400
它的颜色变得更蓝

287
00:04:52,700 --> 00:04:56,566
这是燃烧发电植物所需要的

288
00:04:57,066 --> 00:04:59,733
这植物将燃料转化为法力

289
00:04:59,733 --> 00:05:02,266
而代价是卡顿和物品消失

290
00:05:02,966 --> 00:05:05,700
不过法力还是不够

291
00:05:06,100 --> 00:05:08,666
幸运的是有阿斯加德蒲公英

292
00:05:08,666 --> 00:05:11,066
这是一种不会卡顿的花

293
00:05:11,066 --> 00:05:13,033
也没有其他烦人的事情

294
00:05:13,500 --> 00:05:15,966
接下来不是填满魔力池

295
00:05:15,966 --> 00:05:19,400
我们用魔力在祭坛上制造符文

296
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:22,633
在这我们有更顶级的游戏体验

297
00:05:22,633 --> 00:05:26,033
看一堆乱七八糟的道具在石头旁边乱蹦

298
00:05:26,033 --> 00:05:30,266
还要被那些靠着随便几朵花供能的木头玩意射击

299
00:05:30,700 --> 00:05:34,000
既然我们要做十几次符文

300
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,633
每个都有不同的配方

301
00:05:35,633 --> 00:05:40,200
搞自动化完全没必要

302
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,566
一旦它开始闪闪发光

303
00:05:42,566 --> 00:05:45,600
我们可以扔一块石头完成整个过程

304
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:49,566
我们重复这个有趣的过程50次

305
00:05:49,566 --> 00:05:51,700
每个符文都做四个

306
00:05:51,700 --> 00:05:55,166
希望这是最后一次碰它

307
00:05:55,200 --> 00:05:58,366
一旦我们把所有的符文放在神秘祭坛上

308
00:05:58,366 --> 00:06:02,000
我们把它们注魔成泰拉凝聚板

309
00:06:02,200 --> 00:06:04,000
又一次

310
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:06,066
要求我们在上面放四件东西

311
00:06:06,066 --> 00:06:11,233
希望它们不会在不知道要等多久的合成中消失

312
00:06:11,566 --> 00:06:12,866
为了规避风险

313
00:06:12,866 --> 00:06:14,666
我们改用魔力池作为缓冲

314
00:06:14,666 --> 00:06:17,500
用一些火花来让随机的灯亮起来

315
00:06:17,500 --> 00:06:20,966
这样可以牺牲帧率减小卡顿

316
00:06:21,266 --> 00:06:23,800
于是我们得到了一些泰拉钢

317
00:06:24,033 --> 00:06:28,266
我们堆了很多东西来获得可观速度

318
00:06:28,766 --> 00:06:32,266
我们用泰拉钢做的一个精灵传送门

319
00:06:32,266 --> 00:06:36,066
这个传送门能输入垃圾，并输出垃圾

320
00:06:36,533 --> 00:06:37,866
有了那些新垃圾

321
00:06:37,866 --> 00:06:42,033
召唤盖亚所需的盖亚水晶便可以制造了

322
00:06:42,366 --> 00:06:44,033
与mod的其余部分不同

323
00:06:44,033 --> 00:06:47,433
这个Boss外观平平无奇

324
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:51,366
出于某种原因，它免疫投掷物

325
00:06:51,833 --> 00:06:53,033
打败它之后

326
00:06:53,033 --> 00:06:55,366
我们得到了一些盖亚之魂作为回报

327
00:06:55,366 --> 00:06:58,200
用来制作第一个盖亚魂锭

328
00:06:58,200 --> 00:07:00,666
并召唤上个boss的兄弟

329
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:04,433
现在只需要刷一些boss

330
00:07:04,433 --> 00:07:09,433
直到凑够所有致密盖亚板

331
00:07:09,966 --> 00:07:12,000
一旦我们制造了新机器

332
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,300
我们快速制作一个龙蛋

333
00:07:14,300 --> 00:07:14,966
这样

334
00:07:14,966 --> 00:07:18,366
我们就可以用普通材料制作龙血

335
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,000
但是一旦我们尝试这样做

336
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,566
却遇到了一个问题

337
00:07:22,566 --> 00:07:25,033
我们得把这机器升级到三级

338
00:07:25,866 --> 00:07:28,433
这需要双足飞龙聚合机械方块

339
00:07:28,433 --> 00:07:30,166
我们勉强能做

340
00:07:30,366 --> 00:07:32,200
主要问题是

341
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:35,500
我们需要太空采矿模块MK3

342
00:07:36,566 --> 00:07:39,433
虽然制作它不难

343
00:07:39,433 --> 00:07:40,100
使用它

344
00:07:40,100 --> 00:07:43,666
我们还需要MK3太空电梯加速轨道

345
00:07:44,433 --> 00:07:47,666
这些需要一些奇怪的材料

346
00:07:47,666 --> 00:07:51,500
我们将在高科技风的下一集完成

347
00:07:51,866 --> 00:07:54,066
那么教训呢？

348
00:07:54,866 --> 00:07:56,500
是啊，毕竟

349
00:07:56,500 --> 00:08:00,366
奴役蜜蜂或许并非坏事

350
00:08:00,766 --> 00:08:02,166
它们也在进化

351
00:08:02,166 --> 00:08:04,366
能够制造电子产品

352
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:07,366
所以下季来点电动马达蜜蜂

353
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,866
拜拜

354
00:00:59,200 --> 00:01:00,600
（funny：有趣，奇怪；跟原作者聊完，他也想表达反讽的“幽默”的意思）

355
00:06:32,266 --> 00:06:36,066
（*Garbage in, garbage out 是AI领域的重要定律）

